c: 6
v: 164
t: "Nena, “Kodi ine ndifune Ambuye wina osati Mulungu pamene Iye ndi Ambuye wa zinthu zonse? Munthu aliyense adzakolola zipatso za ntchito yake ndipo palibe mzimu umene udzanyamula katundu wa wina wake. Pomaliza nonse mudzabwerera kwa Ambuye wanu; ndipo Iye adzakuuzani zomwe munali kutsutsana.”"